text:
Kaho, Kaho.
Running is dangerous, so at least let's walk quickly.

It would be troublesome if you got injured, so be more careful next time.
â”€ So, what's up?
I saw a hero show on TV earlier...!

Kaho doesn't know about the hero...?
...Could it be a local program?

TV shows vary by region, you know.
Maybe they broadcast regional stuff here too.

What kind of hero was it?
Local heroes often have interesting motifs.

I thought they were showing something I didn't know!
So I came here right away, so I don't know...

If you came right away, it might still be on.
Shall we confirm what kind of hero it is?

It might end soon,
so let's walk quickly! Let's go!
